---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<section class='sidenews-container'>
  <h2 class='news-header'>New</h2>
  <ul class='news-list'>
    <li class='news-item'>
      <a href="/"><h3>Hydrogen VS Electric Cars</h3></a>
      <p>Will hydrogen-fueled cars ever catch up to EVs?</p>
    </li>
    <hr class="divider">
    <li class='news-item'>
      <a href="/"><h3>The Downsides of AI Artistry</h3></a>
      <p>
        What are the possible adverse effects of on-demand AI image generation?
      </p>
    </li>
    <hr class="divider">
    <li class='news-item'>
      <a href="/"><h3>Is VC Funding Drying Up?</h3></a>
      <p>
        Private funding by VC firms is down 50% YOY. We take a look at what that
        means.
      </p>
